title: 23 and Me and Government Conspiracy (with Chandra Russell)

description:
Are genealogy websites secretly collecting Black people's DNA for nefarious purposes. Langston and his guest Chandra Russell (South Side on Comedy Central) take a metaphorical swab and get back some horrifying results.
